FORMAT: 1A

# Musicgeeks
The Musicgeeks API provides songs that have been displayed on the [Musicgeeks.co website](http://musicgeeks.co).

# Group Song
Song-related resources of the Musicgeeks API.

## Songs Collection [/songs{?apikey}]
Collection of all songs.

The collection is returned as an array of JSON objects.  Each object is a song.

+ Parameters
    + apikey (string) ... The API key of the user

