### Get all songs [GET]
+ Response 200
    [Songs Collection][]

## Song [/songs/{slug}{?apikey}]
A song that was featured on the Musicgeeks site.

The song resource has the following attributes:

- id
- url
- slug
- page_title
- song_title
- soundcloud_url
- gif_url
- love
- who_where
- cred
- posted_on

The *id* is set when the song is created in the Musicgeeks API.

+ Parameters
    + apikey (string) ... The API key of the user
    + slug (string) ... The slug of the song used on the site.
+ Model (application/json)
    JSON representation of the song.

    + Body
    
